♪Let mortal ties never fade♪

830
00:41:34,380 --> 00:41:37,030
♪As time quietly slips away♪

831
00:41:37,030 --> 00:41:40,110
♪Don't let us miss growing old together♪

832
00:41:40,880 --> 00:41:43,360
♪May this heart stay true as the first day♪

833
