♪I'll wait through blooms and dew♪

834
00:41:47,310 --> 00:41:52,190
♪Let greed and wrath fade with the wind♪

835
00:41:54,400 --> 00:41:55,240
Leave.

836
00:41:56,480 --> 00:41:59,410
